@startuml state-content-lifecycle
title Content Lifecycle States

[*] --> Draft : Content created

Draft : Metadata entered
Draft : Media upload pending\nor complete
Draft --> PendingReview : Submit for review

PendingReview : Assigned to\nreview board
PendingReview --> Approved : All reviewers\napprove
PendingReview --> Rejected : Reviewers reject

Approved : Ready for\npublication
Approved --> Published : Admin publishes\n(indexed in Meilisearch)

Published : Visible to children
Published : Searchable
Published --> Archived : Admin archives\n(removed from index)

Rejected : Feedback provided
Rejected --> Draft : Creator revises\nand resubmits

Archived : Hidden from users
Archived : Retained in DB
Archived --> Published : Admin republishes

@enduml
